# Occam workers

## Layout

- `http-extract/extract.mjs` — fetch + Readability + Turndown
- `browser-extract/` — Playwright; daemon in `browser-daemon.mjs`
- `shared/lib/` — shared imports; do not duplicate

## Contract

- Worker stdout: **one JSON line/object** for host parser
- stderr: diagnostics only
- No mojibake — UTF-8 end to end

## Quality

- Site tweaks: recipes under `browser-extract/lib/recipes/` — not new MCP tools
- Live URL regressions: add/adjust `corpora/l0-smoke.jsonl` + update `docs/04`, `docs/11`

## Verify

```powershell
.\scripts\run-l0-fast.ps1
# SPA cases: dotnet run --project benchmarks\l0-gate
```
